description: This match pretty much rocks from start to finish. Rain and Izamar are formidable opponents and it is hard to predict who will come out on top. They each take advantage of each others weaknesses as they duke it out. Needless to say - the loser is NOT happy to give up her bands. Round four is a brutal fuck-fest all over the mat with pile-driving, ass fucking, face fucking and more.
title: SUMMER VENGEANCE CONTINUES! Rain and Izamar face off in epic battle!
